                  <h2 class="margin-0">A CLEAN HOME STARTS WITH REAL PEOPLE</h2>
                </div>
                <div
                  data-w-id="0f12b76c-c595-a3fb-49c8-0bee954ca3be"
                  style="opacity:1"
                  class="w-layout-grid grid_book-about"
                >
                  <div class="card_book-about">
                    <div class="image-wrap_book-about">
                      <img
                        src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/692f17afc3743c9cd4b7cac6/6937d9a66b88a8c458db6362_book-about.avif"
                        loading="lazy"
                        alt="Woman using a cordless vacuum cleaner to clean a hardwood floor in a living room."
                        class="image_cover"
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-wrap_book-about">
                      <div class="heading-style-h5">
                        Клинеры в Кишинёве, которым можно доверять
                      </div>
                      <div class="tone-medium">
                        Каждый клинер проверен и застрахован.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="card_book-about">
                    <div class="image-wrap_book-about">
